rows.label: tlk43300046_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh, so I'm not washing and peeling
fast enough for him...? What a louse.

rows.label: tlk43300046_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Gimme an axe instead of this
paring knife and you'll see what
I can do!

rows.label: tlk43300046_02_msg0004
rows.name:
But I'm not about to throw in
the dishrag.

rows.label: tlk43300046_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Not until the lovely Queen Lagert
has tasted my cooking...!
